snippet.title: Gooba Ball - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Gooba Ball is a puzzle game that utilizes physics to achieve the highest score possible—all before you hit the limit, and it's game over!
Use critical thinking to combine two heads of the same type.

Features VchiBan in their boneless and boned forms and a few cuddly cute friends.

Developed by Mon Amiral / VchiBan
NOTE: This is a clone of Suika Game, which was released on mobile.
